<div>
<p>What can I say in praise of that great one?<br />
He is not a Prophet but has come with a book;<br />
The Spiritual <i>Masnavi</i> of Mowlavi<br />
Is the Qur'an in the language of Pahlavi (Persian).</p>
</div>
</blockquote>
<p>(Khawaja Abdul Hamid Irfani, "The Sayings of Rumi and Iqbal", Bazm-e-Rumi, 1976.)</p>
