<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.naghed.net/Maghale_ha/naghshe_khiyal.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.naghed.net/Maghale_ha/naghshe_khiyal.htm" rel="nofollow">The Rubaiyat of Rumi</a> Lecture of <a href="/wiki/Khosro_Naghed" title="Khosro Naghed">Khosro Naghed</a>.</li>
